single-file, dark-mode LC 4.5 Advanced app that does both â€œbasicâ€ and â€œadvancedâ€ in one toggle.
Save as LCFG-4.5-Advanced.html, open locally, click Import MD, paste your full FG 1â€“1000 Markdown, and go.

