	â€¢	Click â• Add to bundle â†’ choose Hearing / Appeal / Motion â†’ export JSON, copy lines, or Print.
	â€¢	Basic/Advanced toggle trims the UI for speed or opens the full toolkit.
	â€¢	Your dataset + bundle persist in localStorage (offline).
